Our board no longer has any board administrators (see attached screenshot). I understand that a JIRA admin can appoint one but wanted to raise this feedback ticket just in case this came about unintentionally.

*Steps to reproduce:*
# expand the Issue Detail pane for any Issue;
# click the ellipsis (*...*) button and select *More Actions...*;
